"founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1013, "parent_node_name": "mmm"}, "member": {"id": 655340, "username": "kierankihn", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kierankihn", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_mini.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_normal.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_large.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_xlarge.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_xxlarge.png?m=1755360643", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bbaf/89be/655340_xxxlarge.png?m=1755360643", "created": 1697684491, "last_modified": 1755360643, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "qeqv", "last_touched": 1779602063, "title": "吐槽京东自营的罗技售后问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214960", "created": 1779534661, "deleted": 0, "content": "不到一年前在京东买的 MX Master 3s ，最近出现了右键失灵+双击的问题，因为还在保修期内，遂找京东客服。\r\n\r\n在京东上提交售后之后，接到 025-5207-6007 打来的电话，要求我把鼠标寄到当地的罗技售后，并且客服那边把京东的服务单关闭了。另外还要求给京东的服务单好评，才能返寄出的邮费。\r\n\r\n正常的流程不应该是提交服务单之后京东直接上门取件吗，不是很懂为什么需要这么操作。", "content_rendered": "<p>不到一年前在京东买的 MX Master 3s ，最近出现了右键失灵+双击的问题，因为还在保修期内，遂找京东客服。</p>\n<p>在京东上提交售后之后，接到 025-5207-6007 打来的电话，要求我把鼠标寄到当地的罗技售后，并且客服那边把京东的服务单关闭了。另外还要求给京东的服务单好评，才能返寄出的邮费。</p>\n<p>正常的流程不应该是提交服务单之后京东直接上门取件吗，不是很懂为什么需要这么操作。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1779534661, "replies": 30, "id": 1214960}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71199, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9689, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 507014, "username": "wwk", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wwk", "website": "https://lorewild.com", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5582/5951/507014_mini.png?m=1716804778", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5582/5951/507014_normal.png?m=1716804778", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5582/5951/507014_large.png?m=1716804778", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5582/5951/507014_xlarge.png?m=1716804778", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5582/5951/507014_xxlarge.png?m=1716804778", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5582/5951/507014_xxxlarge.png?m=1716804778", "created": 1599463397, "last_modified": 1716804778, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "akira", "last_touched": 1779617493, "title": "让 AI 写产品官网还蛮困难，很磨时间，默认出的文案和样式都不太行，有什么技巧么？ 或者有啥神奇的 skill、prompt 可以提高效率？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1214996", "created": 1779552598, "deleted": 0, "content": "陆陆续续花了接近 3 天时间才改了一版本。\r\n\r\n之前是\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/jU0jggr.png\r\n\r\n\r\n改完现在是\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/dPFGHP3.png\r\n\r\nhttps://i.imgur.com/mnJzFX1.png\r\n\r\n\r\n最初的版本是，AI 直出的文案和样式，文案不说人话，样式也看着着就别扭。\r\n\r\n新版是，每一幕和 AI 描述自己的想法然后定制调出来的，个人感官上舒服了很多。\r\n\r\n然后想着未来可能会用 AI 做更多新产品，手动调也太麻烦了，大家是套模板还是有啥神奇的 skill 或 prompt 可以提高效率么？求分享。\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n另外自荐产品\r\n名字：叙野 Lorewild \r\n网址： https://lorewild.com\r\n推特： https://x.com/ethan180953\r\n\r\n定位是“用 AI 故事学外语”和“AI 角色对话学外语”，支持中文、英语、日语、韩语、德语、西班牙语六个语言。类似酒馆，也可以自建角色和剧本，目前提供了轻量的学习层。\r\n\r\nmd ，一点流量没有，得多尝试 build in public 啥的整起来。", "content_rendered": "陆陆续续花了接近 3 天时间才改了一版本。<br /><br />之前是<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jU0jggr.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jU0jggr.png\" class=\"e